<concept id="concept_ECC89F305B804372B63C3CE67448FB07"> 
  <title>Getting Started with Adobe Marketing Cloud</title> 
  <shortdesc> <?xm-replace_text Short Description?>
  </shortdesc> 
  <prolog> 
	 <metadata> 
		<othermeta name="solution" content="Marketing Cloud"/> </metadata>
  </prolog> 
  <conbody> 
	 <p>The Marketing Cloud is an integrated family of digital marketing
		solutions, as well as an intuitive interface for new resources and
		capabilities, called 
		<term>core services</term>, for your business. 
	 </p> 
	 <p> Marketing Cloud Core Services include: 
	 </p> 
	 <ul id="ul_C816F881A57549AF82160ADB0CC903B5"> 
		<li id="li_690A6006ACBE4F63A6ACD5D25362E5A3"><xref
		  href="access.xml#concept_DFCB29A3B4834FC59AA29E0BBA301584" format="dita"
		  scope="local">Single sign-on</xref> with your Adobe ID to all your digital
		  marketing solutions 
		</li> 
		<li id="li_AB5BD3A35D404CDB8499929E32B5EF5D"><xref
		  href="boards.xml#concept_52E7E7B015D14E2C852D9618CF76860F" format="dita"
		  scope="local">Collaboration features</xref> 
		</li> 
		<li id="li_E09B137668BC4612AD6ABA5C0976935E"><xref
		  href="asset.xml#concept_AD6B33B2C36B4AB38343E0FE1DE18E3B" format="dita"
		  scope="local">Asset sharing</xref> 
		</li> 
		<li id="li_96512257DF6248F2B41FACA8B1523CA6"><xref
		  href="https://marketing.adobe.com/resources/help/en_US/dtm/" format="https"
		  scope="external">Dynamic tag management</xref> 
		</li> 
		<li id="li_3F246466C1E64FF0A9BDF8863733E3E1"><xref
		  href="audiences.xml#concept_F31D8B62FD5144E181979C3A300336A5" format="dita"
		  scope="local">Audience services</xref> 
		</li> 
		<li id="li_61B02BA4AC7845E992372E6BEFE5B045">Authentication using 
		  <xref
			href="https://developer.omniture.com/en_US/documentation/authentication/auth-overview"
			format="https" scope="external">OAuth2</xref>, calling the web services APIs 
		</li> 
	 </ul> 
	 <p> 
		<xref
		 href="http://www.adobe.com/solutions/digital-marketing.html" format="http"
		 scope="external">View an overview video of the Marketing Cloud</xref>. 
	 </p> 
	 <section id="section_AFFBC9EDDE5B4E4493A7C2896121A773"> 
		<table outputclass="simpletable"
		 id="table_5E612F746A704FE095B809A013EE977F"> 
